Package: stigmaR
Title: Measuring and calculating structural stigma
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Seungju", "Kim", , "follhim@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides researchers with pre-computed, state-level structural
    stigma scores derived from publicly available data. Users can merge 
    stigma indices—including implicit bias, explicit attitudes, policies, and belief items—into their own data frames 
    using a single function call.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
URL: https://github.com/stigmaRverse/stigmaR, https://stigmaRverse.github.io/stigmaR/
BugReports: https://github.com/stigmaRverse/stigmaR/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr
LazyData: true
